mermaid
Copy
flowchart TD
    Landing[index.html (Public Landing)]
    WebApp[/web/ (SPA App)]
    Admin[/admin/]
    Auth[/auth/]
    Chat[/chat/]
    RBAC[/rbac/]
    Logger[/logger/]
    Theme[/theme/]
    Orchestrator[/orchestrator/]
    Docs[/docs/]
    Shared[/shared/]
    API[/api/]
    Scripts[/scripts/]
